{"tid":1270653,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"現場嘅巴絲一齊捉狗","createTime":"2019-07-01T01:57:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-01T03:24:35.000Z","uid":71085,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"f92bc53427383200214064fa6a8ab5e5c5279481","tid":1270653,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:57:08.000Z","msg":"頭先同朋友組隊，起碼捉到三隻狗/廢老影人相<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家一見到可疑人士，唔洗怕，大嗌<span style=\"color: red;\">「唔好影相」</span>，會馬上有好多人嚟支援</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">同埋千萬千萬一定一定要<span style=\"color: red;\">戴口罩！</span></span><br />\n眼見好多人都唔戴，大家見到都麻煩提一提"},{"pid":"e503ada02e33d9b91a1ce6d04af210f7c3624db4","tid":1270653,"uid":71085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T01:58:03.000Z","msg":"同埋頭先有個鬼佬一直影相，叫極都唔停，大家都小心（當時得我，無人支援）"},{"pid":"bd11262a98ab0fb73990e9c835ec1a259afa02bf","tid":1270653,"uid":71085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:09:47.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">得閒嘅巴絲上嚟中信橋一齊捉</span></span>"},{"pid":"25739508715b6cd6671a936b74b059454a8508d0","tid":1270653,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3dc8506fdf9f59914487bcf2f01ad3a7b1f13263","tid":1270653,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:15:19.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n見到有可疑 大嗌 唔好怕"},{"pid":"93abba419d13761b891d25308c9034b475378727","tid":1270653,"uid":250951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:18:47.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"d583d831c4165b7d056b0b8e8bf2b70e7b6dc8cb","tid":1270653,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:26:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f7244feb6fc8747fa62235ab49c54f8574116ac3","tid":1270653,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-01T02:35:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bcf1948235b8ef4a77777ceab